Text.LocalizedString: Technology is cool and all, but nothing beats a good big-band show.

Text.SourceString: I’ve been working out extra lately. Can you tell?
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve been working out extra lately. Can you tell?

Text.SourceString: Would you help me pick out an artifact to send back to my mom sometime?//No pressure or anything. I just think you two have the same taste.//<portrait=blushing> She’d probably love anything you pick out.
Text.LocalizedString: Would you help me pick out an artifact to send back to my mom sometime?//No pressure or anything. I just think you two have the same taste.//<portrait=blushing> She’d probably love anything you pick out.

Text.SourceString: Days like this are perfect for cuddling on the sofa with someone special.//<portrait=blushing>Interested, <PlayerName>$Player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Days like this are perfect for cuddling on the sofa with someone special.//<portrait=blushing>Interested, <PlayerName>$Player</>?

Text.SourceString: We can… If you want to.
Text.LocalizedString: We can… If you want to.

Text.SourceString: It’s nice and toasty here. In the mood for something hot?//<portrait=surprised02>To drink, I mean!
Text.LocalizedString: It’s nice and toasty here. In the mood for something hot?//<portrait=surprised02>To drink, I mean!

Text.SourceString: Everyone stay close in here so we can keep warm!//<portrait=blushing>And also so I don’t have to shout.
Text.LocalizedString: Everyone stay close in here so we can keep warm!//<portrait=blushing>And also so I don’t have to shout.

Text.SourceString: Speaking of… You smell really nice up close, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//This is the best part about snowy days…
Text.LocalizedString: Speaking of… You smell really nice up close, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//This is the best part about snowy days…

Text.SourceString: I don’t think I’ll ever be a fan of cold Winters, but I guess that’s just how it goes. Some people love them, and some people don’t.//<portrait=blushing>I wouldn’t mind if…if someone had to keep my hands warm.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t think I’ll ever be a fan of cold Winters, but I guess that’s just how it goes. Some people love them, and some people don’t.//<portrait=blushing>I wouldn’t mind if…if someone had to keep my hands warm.

Text.SourceString: This would be an excellent place for a date, you know.//Just you, me, and thousands of years of history all around us.
Text.LocalizedString: This would be an excellent place for a date, you know.//Just you, me, and thousands of years of history all around us.

Text.SourceString: I’ve never met anyone else who likes the cavern as much as I do.//<portrait=concerned><NPCName>Zarah’s</> down here a lot, but she’s looking for adventure, not treasure.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve never met anyone else who likes the cavern as much as I do.//<portrait=concerned><NPCName>Zarah’s</> down here a lot, but she’s looking for adventure, not treasure.

Text.SourceString: It’s nice… We have lots in common.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s nice… We have lots in common.

Text.SourceString: I swear, I <Italic>knew</> I’d run into you here.//<portrait=normal>Odd, isn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: I swear, I <Italic>knew</> I’d run into you here.//<portrait=normal>Odd, isn’t it?

Text.SourceString: I always have a great time here, but we need some new stuff on the menu.//Maybe I should tell <NPCName>Frank</> about that okra and turnip drink I came up with.
Text.LocalizedString: I always have a great time here, but we need some new stuff on the menu.//Maybe I should tell <NPCName>Frank</> about that okra and turnip drink I came up with.

Text.SourceString: I don’t know about you, but I’m counting down the days until Summer is finally here.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t know about you, but I’m counting down the days until Summer is finally here.

Text.SourceString: There’s just something about holding an artifact in your hands and imagining all the people and events it’s seen.
Text.LocalizedString: There’s just something about holding an artifact in your hands and imagining all the people and events it’s seen.

Text.SourceString: I think artifacts are an incredible way to connect with the past and gain a deeper understanding of the world we live in. Agree?
Text.LocalizedString: I think artifacts are an incredible way to connect with the past and gain a deeper understanding of the world we live in. Agree?

Text.SourceString: I don’t know about you, but I could spend hours in a museum looking at artifacts and learning about their history.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t know about you, but I could spend hours in a museum looking at artifacts and learning about their history.

Text.SourceString: If you haven’t tried <NPCName>Frank</>’s mystery dish yet, you’re definitely missing out. It’s an experience you won’t forget.
